    <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1497366216548-37526070297c">
    <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1502005229762-cf1b2da7c5d6">
    <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1503387762-592deb58ef4e">
  </div>
</section>

<section class="why">
  <h2>What Clients Say</h2>
  <div class="grid">
    <div class="testimonial">“Best contractor I’ve worked with. Clean, fast, and professional.”</div>
    <div class="testimonial">“Finished my home remodel ahead of schedule.”</div>
